2. improve  —  © 2026 shadcn
   Source: https://github.com/shadcn/improve  (skills/improve)
================================================================================

`explore` derives its read-only advisor discipline, Hard Rules, evidence rule,
recon→audit/explore→vet→produce workflow, and subagent fan-out pattern from the
`improve` skill, and **vendors and adapts** three of its reference documents
(plan output directory changed from `plans/` to `docs/plans/`, plus
explore-context headers):

  - skills/explore/references/plan-template.md       (vendored & adapted)
  - skills/explore/references/audit-playbook.md      (vendored)
  - skills/explore/references/closing-the-loop.md    (vendored & adapted)

