3. caveman  —  © 2026 Julius Brussee
   Source: https://github.com/JuliusBrussee/caveman
================================================================================

`explore`'s `--caveman` flag follows the token-compression convention of the
`caveman` skill (intensity levels lite / full / ultra / wenyan-*, the
drop-fluff-keep-substance rules, and the auto-clarity exceptions). The
convention is described in explore's own words in
`skills/explore/references/caveman.md`; no `caveman` source file is reproduced
verbatim. This notice is included as attribution and good practice.

